Revision history for Syndicate

{{$NEXT}}

    - Initial release. Syndication feed parser and generator for
      RSS 2.0, RSS 0.91, RSS 1.0 (RDF), Atom 1.0, and JSON Feed 1.1.

    [Formats]
    - RSS 2.0 parsing, generation, and XML output
    - RSS 0.91 parsing, generation, and XML output
    - RSS 1.0 (RDF) parsing, generation, and XML output
    - Atom 1.0 parsing, full XML output with all fields and entity handling
    - JSON Feed 1.1 parsing and JSON generation

    [API]
    - Syndicate::Builder::Feed and Syndicate::Builder::Entry for
      format-agnostic feed construction
    - Unified Syndicate.parse, feed-format, and parse-feed entry points
    - Syndicate::Feed role with $.title, $.link, $.description,
      $.generator, $.language, @.items
    - Syndicate::Item role with $.title, $.link, $.summary, $.author,
      $.updated, $.id, $.content
    - Syndicate::Discovery for feed URL discovery from HTML pages
    - Syndicate::Stats for thread-safe parsing statistics

    [Extensions]
    - Dublin Core (dc:creator, dc:date, dc:subject)
    - Media RSS (media:content, media:thumbnail, media:title,
      media:description)
    - iTunes podcast (itunes:author, itunes:summary, itunes:duration)

    [Testing]
    - 13 test files with 483 assertions covering parsing, generation,
      roundtrip, builder API, feed discovery, extensions, and concurrency
